title: 820-3209  memory test fail
message: Computer came in with no power or charge light, I replaced a bunch of corroded components around L9701 which brought it back to life, seems to run okay but it fails about half the memory tests in ASD.  Anything I can do about this?

title: 820-3209  memory test fail
message: Hmmm, I would first see if there are any issues when in normal use. It could be corrosion under RAM or CPU or just ASD being shit.
